    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104880/extras/75ed159b7874dbf4963456bfd8b764a9.poster.avif?t=1744437116\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104880/extras/75ed159b7874dbf4963456bfd8b764a9.webm?t=1744437116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104880/extras/75ed159b7874dbf4963456bfd8b764a9.mp4?t=1744437116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>撕碎梦境世界！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款独立解谜游戏中，你将扮演梦神卡萨里。你的任务是像反向拼图一样将梦境分解成碎片，然后用这些碎片重新组装新的梦境，帮助沉睡中的角色理解自己并克服生活中的挑战。游戏结合了可爱而略显阴森的氛围，以及以漫画风格呈现的故事情节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104880/extras/18ef38e4fe0fdc8c6d6d0f4ee20432e2.avif?t=1744437116\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的机制：你不仅要寻找物品，还要将梦境分解成组件，找到所有隐藏的元素。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度故事情节：每个梦境都是一个独特的故事，你与卡萨里一起帮助角色克服内心的冲突，找到自己的道路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的视觉风格：手绘插图和引人入胜的漫画风格为游戏增添了特别的氛围。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104880/extras/91c915562aa7d3983061ccc9d9d0608d.avif?t=1744437116\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦境世界在等待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助角色找到重要问题的答案，并体验他们梦境中的难忘旅程。</p>",
